<apex:page renderAs="pdf" controller="GOPDeclineLetterCtrl">
    <!--<apex:stylesheet value="{!URLFOR($Resource.GOPPDFStyle, 'footer.css')}"/>-->
    <apex:stylesheet value="{!$Resource.PDFDocumentStyle}" />
        <c:PDFHeaderFooter type="footer" position="center">
            <div class="footer" style="text-align: center; font-size: 7pt; color: #333">
                <div style="border-top: .25pt solid #666; font-family: 'Arial Unicode MS';">
                Confidential, unpublished property of Cigna. Do not duplicate or distribute. Use and distribution limited solely to authorized personnel.<br/>
                Cigna Worldwide General Insurance Company Limited 信諾環球保險有限公司
            </div>
            </div>    
    </c:PDFHeaderFooter>
    <head>
        <style>
            div, table, tr, td{
            font-family: Arial Unicode MS, sans-serif;
            font-size:14px;
            }
             .rTable { 
                display: table; 
                width: 100%;
                float: left;
               
            }
            .rTableRow { 
                display: table-row; 
            }
            .rTableCell { 
              
                display: table-cell; 
                border-collapse: collapse;
               
                padding:5px;
                width: 25%;
                word-break: break-word !important; /* IE */
               
                 white-space: pre-wrap;      /* CSS3 */   
                 white-space: -moz-pre-wrap; /* Firefox */    
                 white-space: -pre-wrap;     /* before Opera 7 */   
                 white-space: -o-pre-wrap;   /* Opera 7 */    
               
            }
            @page{
            page-break-after:always;
            }
            
        </style>
    </head>
    
    <div style="width: 100%;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <b>Letter relating to application for Cashless Medical Service (CMS)</b><br/>
            <b>有關Cashless Medical Service (CMS)申請</b>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div style="position:absolute;right:0;top:25px;width:10%;float:right">
        <apex:image url="{!$Resource.Cigna_Logo}" width="50" height="50"/>
        <br/>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!showForPerson}">
        <div style="text-align: center;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <u><b>Letter to Person Insured</b></u><br/>
            <u><b>致受保人的信件</b></u><br/>
        </div>
    </apex:outputPanel>
    <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!!showForPerson}">
        <div style="text-align: center;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <u><b>Letter to Hospital/Clinic</b></u><br/>
            <u><b>致醫院/診所的信件</b></u><br/>
        </div>
    </apex:outputPanel>
    
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <apex:outputPanel id="information">
        <table style="width: 100%;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%"><u>Date of Letter信件日期:{!dateOfLetter}</u></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%"><u>Reference number of application for CMS 申請個案編號:{!caseNumber}</u></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <table style="width: 100%;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;<u><b>Policy's Particulars保單資料</b></u></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Name of insurance plan保單名稱:{!productName}</u></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Policy number保單號碼:{!policyNumber}</u></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;<u><b>Person Insured’s Particular受保人資料</b></u></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <table style="width:100%;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Person Insured's Name受保人姓名:{!patientName}</td>
                    <td>Person Insured's HKID受保人香港身分證:{!patientHKIDNo}</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <table style="width: 100%;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;<u><b>Treatment Details治療詳情</b></u></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <br/>
        <div style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            &nbsp;&nbsp;Diagnosis診斷:
            <ol>
                <apex:repeat value="{!diagnosisDescr}" var="diag" id="diagRepeat">
                    <li>{!diag}</li>
                </apex:repeat>
            </ol>
            &nbsp;&nbsp;Procedure(s)治療程序:
            <ol>
                <apex:repeat value="{!CPTDescr}" var="cpt" id="cptRepeat">
                    <li>{!cpt}</li>
                </apex:repeat>
            </ol>
            
        </div>
        <br/>
        <table style="width:100%;font-family: Arial Unicode MS">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>Admission date入院日期:{!addminsionDate}</td>
                    <td>Estimated length of stay預計住院日數:{!cignaExpectedLOS}</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <table width="100%" style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">Hospital醫院/Clinic診所:{!hospitalName} </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">Booked class of ward病房級別:{!wardClass} </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;<u><b>Physician’s Particulars醫生資料</b></u></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="width: 100%">&nbsp;</td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <table style="width:100%;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Doctor’s name醫生姓名:{!physicianName} </td>
                    <td>Email Address電郵地址:{!physicianEmail} </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>&nbsp;&nbsp;Tel. number電話號碼:{!physicianContactNo} </td>
                    <td>Fax number傳真號碼:{!physicianFaxNo} </td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <br/><br/>
        <div style="page-break-before:always;font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:13.5px;">
            <span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u><b>Result of CMS Application申請結果</b></u></span>
            <ul style="list-style-type:none">
                <li>After careful consideration, we regret to inform you that the Person Insured’s application for the CMS in respect of the above-mentioned surgery(ies)/treatment(s)/investigation(s) is <u><b>DECLINED</b></u> <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!showForPerson}">  due to <br/><u><b>{!commercialDeniedReasonEng}</b></u></apex:outputPanel></li>
                <li style="width: 100%">&nbsp;</li>
                <li>經過慎重考慮後，我們遺憾地通知您，受保人就上述手術/治療/檢驗提出的CMS申請因<u><b>已被拒絕</b></u>。<apex:outputPanel rendered="{!showForPerson}">（原因：<u><br/> <div class="rTableRow"><div class="rTableCell" style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:13.5px;">{!commercialDeniedReasonChi}</div></div></u>）</apex:outputPanel></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <br/><br/>
        <div style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <span><u><b>Remarks:</b></u></span><br/><br/>       
            <ol type="1">
                <li>If the Person Insured has any new or additional documents and information relevant to his/her application for CMS and would like to request for a re-assessment of his/her application for CMS, the Person Insured can send an email to Cigna: preauthhk@cigna.com attaching such new or additional documents and information to Cigna for consideration.</li>
                <li>Cigna has the sole and absolute discretion in relation to all matters arising from or in connection with this CMS application, and that in the event of disputes, the decision of Cigna shall be final.</li>
                <li>Cigna has the sole and absolute right to amend, vary, suspend and/or cancel any Cashless Medical Service from time to time and at any time without prior notice.</li>
                <li>In case of discrepancies between the English version and the Chinese version of this letter, the English version shall apply and prevail.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <br/><br/>
        <div style="font-family: Arial Unicode MS;font-size:14px;">
            <span><u><b>備注</b></u></span><br/><br/>     
            <ol type="1">
                <li>如果受保人有任何與其申請CMS&nbsp;相關的新補充文件和資訊，並希望要求重新評估其CMS&nbsp;申請，受保人可以將&nbsp; 此類補充文件和資訊透過電子郵件提交予信諾環球:&nbsp;preauthhk@cigna.com作考慮。</li>
                <li>信諾環球對於由本&nbsp;CMS&nbsp;申請引起或與之相關的所有事宜擁有唯一且絕對決定權，如有爭議，信諾環球的決定 將為最終決定。</li>
                <li>信諾環球擁有隨時修改、變更、暫停和/或取消任何CMS的唯一且絕對權利，恕不另行通知。</li>
                <li>此信函備有中英文版本，如內容有異，以英文版本為準。</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </apex:outputPanel>
</apex:page>